data.description: Welcome to 211 Weeping Cypress Drive, your dream home awaits! This property offers the perfect blend of elegance and comfort. With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, there's plenty of space for the whole family. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors and tall ceilings that create an inviting atmosphere throughout. The kitchen features rich and open spaces, along with beautiful countertops that are both stylish and functional. One of the highlights of this home is the spacious sunroom, located just off the family room. It's the perfect spot to relax and soak up the natural light while enjoying a cup of coffee or reading your favorite book. In the family living room, a gas log fireplace adds both ambience and warmth on cozy evenings.Need a quiet space to work or study? Look no further than the well-equipped study on the first floor. The large owner's suite boasts a spacious sitting room, walk-in closet, and a fully equipped bathroom complete with a garden soaking tub - perfect for unwinding after a long day. Outside, you'll find a fenced-in backyard that's ideal for pets to roam freely. The patio area is complete with an outdoor fireplace, creating an inviting space for making lasting family memories or entertaining guests. Living in this community also comes with its perks! Enjoy hours of warm weather entertainment at the community pool located directly behind the home. Plus, with its great location, you'll have easy access to a wide variety of stores, restaurants, and services - everything you need is just moments away. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call 211 Weeping Cypress Drive your new home. Schedule your showing today and start living your dream!
